RetrieveStateroomDetail with brand, shipCode, sailDate, cabinNumber

con:config.con:query: SELECT TOP 5 baship AS Ship_Code, bacbno AS Stateroom_Number FROM AS400_Mirror.dbo.ICSCBD B INNER JOIN AS400_Mirror.dbo.ICSHPD S ON B.BASHIP = S.SHSHIP INNER JOIN AS400_Mirror.dbo.ICCTCD ON LKCATG = B.BACBIO AND (LKBRND = SHBRND) INNER JOIN AS400_Mirror.dbo.ICCTPD ON B.BASHIP = ARSHIP AND B.BACTYP = ARCTYP INNER JOIN AS400_Mirror.dbo.ICDCKD D ON B.BADKCD = AQDKCD AND B.BASHIP = AQSHIP WHERE (S.SHPBRD LIKE 'R') AND b.bacbdd = '0' -- cabin delete date AND (B.BAEFDT = (SELECT MAX(BAEFDT) FROM AS400_Mirror.dbo.ICSCBD WHERE BASHIP = B.BASHIP AND BAEFDT <= 1190305 AND BACBNO = B.BACBNO));
